text: Santiago Centenera (born 5 November 1961) is a Spanish equestrian. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Spain Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Madrid
